Interface ViewI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IsaacViewI
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    @Contract
public interface ViewI
extends IsaacViewI
    ViewI Extends the basic IsaacViewI (which only provides menu hooks) to add a Region view area, which could be embedded into another view.
